{
  "slug": "discord",
  "name": "Discord",
  "type": "plugin",
  "description": "Discord channel for Claude Code — messaging bridge with built-in access control. Manage pairing, allowlists, and policy via /discord:access.",
  "longDescription": "Ships **1 MCP server** and **2 skills** (`/discord:configure`, `/discord:access`). The MCP server provides **5 tools**: `reply` (text + up to 10 file attachments, 25MB each), `react` (Unicode/custom emoji), `edit_message`, `fetch_messages` (up to 100 per channel), and `download_attachment`. Access control supports DM pairing, guild channels, allowlists, and mention detection — all configurable per Discord snowflake ID via `access.json`. Runs on Bun; shows typing indicators while Claude processes responses.",
